org.eclipse.golo.compiler.ir

Interface Scope

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Block, CaseStatement, ConditionalBranching, ForEachLoopStatement, GoloFunction, LoopStatement, ReferenceTable, ReturnStatement

    public interface Scope
    Interface for all IR elements that have a scope (a ReferenceTable) (or encapsulate something that have one).
